                  letter-spacing:4px;color:#c9a84c;margin-bottom:6px;">Legacy Power</div>
      <div style="font-family:'Cinzel',serif;font-size:22px;color:white;font-weight:900;
                  text-shadow:0 0 30px rgba(201,168,76,0.8);">Champion's Call</div>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:#8892a4;margin-top:8px;font-style:italic;">
        A past champion guides your hand...
      </div>
